.rule_1_9_1_3_ensure_trusted_ntp_server_exists

Reference: al/asa-96-general-config/basic-hostname-pw.html

Remediation: 
Step 1: Acquire the authentication key ID <key_id>, the IP address of the NTP server
<ip_address> and the interface <interface_name> used by the appliance to
communicate with the NTP server.

Step 2: Run the following to configure the trusted NTP server
hostname(config)# ntp server <ip_address> key <key_id> source
<interface_name>

